{"title":"“一线”之声","authors":["郑俊华"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":5,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“一线”之声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郑俊华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是一条船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"承载着父兄的厚望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和母亲的祈愿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我　是一只鹰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在人们热切守望的天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"振翅飞旋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我　是一片叶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就要在最高的枝头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"栉风沐雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我　是一滴水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就要在风口浪尖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——斗险"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请转告我的小女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让她穿上最靓丽的春装"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来与阴霾相抗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请转告我的父兄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让他们用咏春的诗句"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来把激情点燃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告诉我妻　我是她的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她永远的骄傲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告诉我的战友吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和千千万万的我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与他携手并肩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"力排非典"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共赴一线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让魔鬼在“天使”的面前"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"震颤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个眼神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是一份鼓舞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个微笑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是一声共勉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我们挺胸昂首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"面对发生在春天里的挑衅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大声地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向全世界宣布"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——应战！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":16,"page_end":16}